{"tid":1953600,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"居屋問題","createTime":"2020-04-01T09:12:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T15:38:04.000Z","uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b493ae6e1ead21cea632ed512c1dd77022470075","tid":1953600,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T09:12:17.000Z","msg":"如果未補地價，售價寫390萬，實際即係要比幾錢買？thanks"},{"pid":"d212f2349010c217a4e63a1d8172b5868f19c8f0","tid":1953600,"uid":188198,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:15:08.000Z","msg":"390 over番0.6，因為你白表買要幫佢補埋地價(好似係)"},{"pid":"ef5bde9a6486748e6af853513024b05f2980af89","tid":1953600,"uid":36563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T11:54:37.000Z","msg":"好似唔同屋苑個補價率係唔同的"},{"pid":"42cf3e35f22f1889e288b3914e738c714780427b","tid":1953600,"uid":24344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T11:55:59.000Z","msg":"預比多150萬左右"},{"pid":"6e10d0046178a5707e40be535fa5c58c9c8de9e2","tid":1953600,"uid":162567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b493ae6e1ead21cea632ed512c1dd77022470075","tid":1953600,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T09:12:17.000Z","msg":"如果未補地價，售價寫390萬，實際即係要比幾錢買？thanks"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:02:56.000Z","msg":"如果唔還價，你綠表咪390萬囉<br />\n白表就多at least 150萬"},{"pid":"0a672af4a41b0ae5d22e8034f7bd7b4bda9c4105","tid":1953600,"uid":94290,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d212f2349010c217a4e63a1d8172b5868f19c8f0","tid":1953600,"uid":188198,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:15:08.000Z","msg":"390 over番0.6，因為你白表買要幫佢補埋地價(好似係)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:44:13.000Z","msg":"白表買邊洗補地價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ea0c3cabe42816e47e6c55b18a4ce919bc7930","tid":1953600,"uid":188198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a672af4a41b0ae5d22e8034f7bd7b4bda9c4105","tid":1953600,"uid":94290,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d212f2349010c217a4e63a1d8172b5868f19c8f0","tid":1953600,"uid":188198,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:15:08.000Z","msg":"390 over番0.6，因為你白表買要幫佢補埋地價(好似係)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:44:13.000Z","msg":"白表買邊洗補地價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:46:36.000Z","msg":"樓主個case似係白表想買未補價居屋，咁咪要補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d926d155bb4c7c438c001ebcddc138aab9604813","tid":1953600,"uid":169895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74ea0c3cabe42816e47e6c55b18a4ce919bc7930","tid":1953600,"uid":188198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a672af4a41b0ae5d22e8034f7bd7b4bda9c4105","tid":1953600,"uid":94290,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d212f2349010c217a4e63a1d8172b5868f19c8f0","tid":1953600,"uid":188198,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:15:08.000Z","msg":"390 over番0.6，因為你白表買要幫佢補埋地價(好似係)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:44:13.000Z","msg":"白表買邊洗補地價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:46:36.000Z","msg":"樓主個case似係白表想買未補價居屋，咁咪要補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:06:26.000Z","msg":"白表唔洗補地價"},{"pid":"e011c2210018b20c657da64b3271f660e91ab94b","tid":1953600,"uid":169895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:07:40.000Z","msg":"補地價如何計算？<br />\n補地價的計算其實並不複雜，看看以下公式就會明白：<br />\n<br />\n補價 = 補價時之市值 x [(購入時之十足市值－購入時樓價) / 購入時之十足市值] x 100%<br />\n<br />\n換句話講，<br />\n<br />\n補價 = 補價時之市值 x 購入時政府提供之折扣率<br />\n<br />\n假設居屋當時售價HK$245萬，當時以市價7折出售，即當時之十足市值為350萬元，目前該單位市值已升至HK$500萬，現時補價計算如下：<br />\n<br />\nHK$500萬 x [(HK$350萬 &ndash; HK$245萬) / HK$250萬] x 100%<br />\n<br />\n= HK$500萬 x 30%<br />\n<br />\n= HK$150萬<br />\n<br />\n要留意的是，補價時之市值並非你、我、買家或地產代理決定，要由房委會委託之估價行來評定。另外，居屋或其他資助出售房屋的折扣率不一定是30%，即使是同一屋苑或屋邨，不同單位的折扣率也有出入，完全是取決於房委會於不同時期的推售策略。"},{"pid":"1d738aa29aa6b718aadd2d945d93f87593535f14","tid":1953600,"uid":169895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:10:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/home-ownership/hos-secondary-market/available-hos-courts/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.housingauthority.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fhome-ownership%2Fhos-secondary-market%2Favailable-hos-courts%2Findex.html&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=e488bf44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/home-ownership/hos-secondary-market/available-hos-courts/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n可供購買的居屋屋苑"},{"pid":"30a85042f62c573a37b3ea17db74afd76317b552","tid":1953600,"uid":188198,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d926d155bb4c7c438c001ebcddc138aab9604813","tid":1953600,"uid":169895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74ea0c3cabe42816e47e6c55b18a4ce919bc7930","tid":1953600,"uid":188198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a672af4a41b0ae5d22e8034f7bd7b4bda9c4105","tid":1953600,"uid":94290,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:44:13.000Z","msg":"白表買邊洗補地價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:46:36.000Z","msg":"樓主個case似係白表想買未補價居屋，咁咪要補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:06:26.000Z","msg":"白表唔洗補地價"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:13:01.000Z","msg":"你地岩，白表=白居二表<br />\n我成日理解錯白表係咩表都無的買家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如樓主咩表都無(白居二,綠表,公屋)，就要幫人補地價"},{"pid":"e31a459d039772dc5723ce3d72e9d9ae55c02236","tid":1953600,"uid":9230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"30a85042f62c573a37b3ea17db74afd76317b552","tid":1953600,"uid":188198,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d926d155bb4c7c438c001ebcddc138aab9604813","tid":1953600,"uid":169895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74ea0c3cabe42816e47e6c55b18a4ce919bc7930","tid":1953600,"uid":188198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:46:36.000Z","msg":"樓主個case似係白表想買未補價居屋，咁咪要補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:06:26.000Z","msg":"白表唔洗補地價"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:13:01.000Z","msg":"你地岩，白表=白居二表<br />\n我成日理解錯白表係咩表都無的買家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如樓主咩表都無(白居二,綠表,公屋)，就要幫人補地價"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:20:58.000Z","msg":"大佬！白居易係=綠表資格呀<br />\n<br />\n綠表價 = 未補地價，除非以提名形式提名一個合資助資格人士，然後得到房屋署署長批准，方可買賣<br />\n<br />\n所以綠表、白居易雙方會有準買證同準賣證同提名信<br />\n<br />\n俗稱白表價，即係自由市場價，即物業已向政府補地價（或者限售條款已届滿），可以自由在市場買賣"},{"pid":"fe13597e020e7f7ff4e6f5fc0256b6538dcc69a2","tid":1953600,"uid":24344,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"30a85042f62c573a37b3ea17db74afd76317b552","tid":1953600,"uid":188198,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d926d155bb4c7c438c001ebcddc138aab9604813","tid":1953600,"uid":169895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74ea0c3cabe42816e47e6c55b18a4ce919bc7930","tid":1953600,"uid":188198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:46:36.000Z","msg":"樓主個case似係白表想買未補價居屋，咁咪要補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:06:26.000Z","msg":"白表唔洗補地價"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:13:01.000Z","msg":"你地岩，白表=白居二表<br />\n我成日理解錯白表係咩表都無的買家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如樓主咩表都無(白居二,綠表,公屋)，就要幫人補地價"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16:30:13.000Z","msg":"你無理解錯根本就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n綠表=本身係公屋戶主或即將輪候到公屋嘅人（可以用免補地價嘅價錢購買）<br />\n<br />\n白表=咩都無的人（要補返地價先可以購買）<br />\n<br />\n白居二=抽中左白表居屋第二市場計劃的人，可以一年內購買免補地價嘅公屋居屋）"},{"pid":"0ce93d49abfe81688d5dbb5dc1b43fed48919436","tid":1953600,"uid":110992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d212f2349010c217a4e63a1d8172b5868f19c8f0","tid":1953600,"uid":188198,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:15:08.000Z","msg":"390 over番0.6，因為你白表買要幫佢補埋地價(好似係)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16:33:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12481514b00f1f5dc370a6b4c97ba9bbf11f198a","tid":1953600,"uid":55222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T03:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e9ec95a27996561203019e30a746a83ae47ff3","tid":1953600,"uid":8929,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T03:39:47.000Z","msg":"白表樓上班on9唔識可唔可以唔好扮識？<br />\n<br />\n綠表=HS/HA租户，買居屋要交番間公屋<br />\n<br />\n白表=街外人向HA申請居屋購買資格買新居屋<br />\n<br />\n白居二=白表居屋二手市場，申請人可以唔補地價買二手居屋<br />\n<br />\n自由市場=已補地價居屋，當私人樓買賣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n笑死"},{"pid":"3d347de6992ddc49018cd953468422b55f11cb6e","tid":1953600,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:24:31.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"7bbd15eeb6fb9e82d0b6b6d41a7dc65197a46e07","tid":1953600,"uid":60109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"12481514b00f1f5dc370a6b4c97ba9bbf11f198a","tid":1953600,"uid":55222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T03:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T06:21:58.000Z","msg":"叫原業主申請補地價，新買家俾錢<br />\n<br />\n我都係咁買居屋"},{"pid":"d796f46d5cd3c74ebac739fd65020587b42ca19f","tid":1953600,"uid":116723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bbd15eeb6fb9e82d0b6b6d41a7dc65197a46e07","tid":